# TripAdvisor Restaurant Reviews - Sentiment Analysis using NLP Models




Requirements.txt file shows the package versions required to run this program. 

Install the packages using : pip install -r requirements.txt

The data for this project is downloaded from the kaggle website. In order to download the data, make sure the kaggle.json authentication file is in your system home drive. 

Kaggle Account and API Key:
Log in to your Kaggle account or create a new one if you don't have an account: https://www.kaggle.com/
After logging in, go to your Kaggle account settings: https://www.kaggle.com/account

    Scroll down to the "API" section and click on "Create New API Token." This will download a file named kaggle.json containing your API key.

b. Configure Kaggle CLI:

Place the downloaded kaggle.json file in the following directory:

    On Windows: C:\Users\<Your-Username>\.kaggle\kaggle.json
    On macOS/Linux: /Users/<Your-Username>/.kaggle/kaggle.json

Make sure to replace <Your-Username> with your actual username.
